### 
### Short leap4 commands.
### 
###   Requires Mark Lillibridge's leap4 API 2.0 already implemented.
### 

include "leap3_short.vch";


## 
## Target: the first (Nth) occurrence of a character:
## 

      <kill> [<count>] <prn> = Leap4($1, $3, When($2,$2,1), x);
shift <leap> [<count>] <prn> = Leap4($1, $3, When($2,$2,1), s);
